Dialogue: 1,0:00:09.11,0:00:10.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备好了吗  孩子们
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.11,0:00:10.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you ready, kids?
Dialogue: 1,0:00:10.53,0:00:12.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了船长
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.53,0:00:12.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Aye aye, captain
Dialogue: 1,0:00:12.36,0:00:13.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我听不见
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.36,0:00:13.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't hear you
Dialogue: 1,0:00:13.82,0:00:15.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了船长
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.82,0:00:15.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Aye aye, captain
Dialogue: 1,0:00:18.74,0:00:21.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是谁住在深海的大菠萝里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.74,0:00:21.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who lives in a pineapple under the sea?
Dialogue: 1,0:00:21.00,0:00:22.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.00,0:00:22.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob SquarePants
Dialogue: 1,0:00:22.79,0:00:24.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,方方黄黄伸缩自如
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.79,0:00:24.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Absorbent and yellow and porous is he
Dialogue: 1,0:00:24.96,0:00:26.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.96,0:00:26.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob SquarePants
Dialogue: 1,0:00:26.79,0:00:29.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,如果四处探险是你的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.79,0:00:29.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If nautical nonsense be something you wish
Dialogue: 1,0:00:29.00,0:00:30.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.00,0:00:30.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob SquarePants
Dialogue: 1,0:00:30.76,0:00:33.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就敲敲甲板让大鱼开路
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.76,0:00:33.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then drop on the deck and flop like a fish
Dialogue: 1,0:00:33.09,0:00:34.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.09,0:00:34.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob SquarePants
Dialogue: 1,0:00:34.26,0:00:34.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.26,0:00:34.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ready
Dialogue: 1,0:00:34.88,0:00:44.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.88,0:00:44.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob SquarePants
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.73,0:00:49.23,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1179.518,406)}海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 1,0:00:52.48,0:00:54.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,又到了新一期
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.48,0:00:54.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's time for another
Dialogue: 1,0:00:54.01,0:00:56.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝特辑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.01,0:00:56.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob SquarePants special
Dialogue: 1,0:00:56.40,0:00:58.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但这次的特辑不一般
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.40,0:00:58.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But it's not an ordinary special
Dialogue: 1,0:00:58.47,0:01:01.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为今天不仅要去加利福尼亚恩斯诺
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.47,0:01:01.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,because today we go to Encino, California
Dialogue: 1,0:01:01.72,0:01:02.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且要穿越回
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.72,0:01:02.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,as it was
Dialogue: 1,0:01:03.49,0:01:06.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一亿年以前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.49,0:01:06.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,100,000,000 years ago
Dialogue: 1,0:01:06.22,0:01:07.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以大家准备好收看
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.22,0:01:07.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So prepare yourself for
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.88,0:01:12.76,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(715.994,202)}海绵史传
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.71,0:01:12.76,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(339.471,838)}史前笑传
Dialogue: 1,0:01:12.77,0:01:15.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有请主持人  海盗派斯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.77,0:01:15.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,With your host, Patchy the Pirate
Dialogue: 1,0:01:22.11,0:01:23.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小朋友们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.11,0:01:23.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, kids
Dialogue: 1,0:01:23.02,0:01:24.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们大概心里正纳闷
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.02,0:01:24.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, you're probably wondering
Dialogue: 1,0:01:24.95,0:01:27.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派斯在山洞里干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.95,0:01:27.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"What's Patchy doing in a cave?"
Dialogue: 1,0:01:27.22,0:01:28.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,问得好  小东西
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.22,0:01:28.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good question, you little
Dialogue: 1,0:01:30.55,0:01:33.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为今天这期海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.55,0:01:33.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, it's because today's SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:01:33.29,0:01:35.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,剧情可是发生在史前时代
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.29,0:01:35.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,takes place in prehistoric times
Dialogue: 1,0:01:35.45,0:01:38.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那时候人类还在艰难求生存
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.45,0:01:38.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,back when man struggled for survival
Dialogue: 1,0:01:38.00,0:01:40.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而统治全地球的则是恐龙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.00,0:01:40.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and dinosaurs ruled the earth
Dialogue: 1,0:01:40.58,0:01:42.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对不对啊  布朗提
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.58,0:01:42.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right, Bronty?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:42.35,0:01:44.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但现在换我骑你了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.35,0:01:44.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But I'm riding you now
Dialogue: 1,0:01:47.37,0:01:48.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,卡住了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.37,0:01:48.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stuck
Dialogue: 1,0:01:51.22,0:01:52.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,救我出来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.22,0:01:52.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get me out
Dialogue: 1,0:01:52.20,0:01:53.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,救命  救命
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.20,0:01:53.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Help, help
Dialogue: 1,0:01:53.21,0:01:55.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,75,,请稍候
Dialogue: 1,0:01:56.13,0:01:57.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我刚刚说到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.13,0:01:57.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Like I was saying
Dialogue: 1,0:01:57.34,0:01:59.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,史前时代好得不能再好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.34,0:01:59.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,prehistoric times were the greatest
Dialogue: 1,0:01:59.30,0:02:02.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个时代更简单  乐趣也简单
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.30,0:02:02.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It was a simpler time, with simpler pleasures
Dialogue: 1,0:02:02.90,0:02:04.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,穿搭早就提前搭好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.90,0:02:04.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your clothes always matched
Dialogue: 1,0:02:05.23,0:02:08.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,往墙上乱画都不会有人骂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.23,0:02:08.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You could draw on the walls and nobody would yell at you
Dialogue: 1,0:02:08.07,0:02:11.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,棒球还更好打了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.07,0:02:11.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It was much easier to hit a baseball
Dialogue: 1,0:02:11.31,0:02:14.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错  史前时代最棒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.31,0:02:14.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah, prehistoric times were the best
Dialogue: 1,0:02:15.21,0:02:16.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小朋友们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.21,0:02:16.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, kids
Dialogue: 1,0:02:16.07,0:02:18.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,外面是传来了翼龙拍翅膀的声音吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.07,0:02:18.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,are those pterodactyl wings I hear a-flapping?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:18.82,0:02:20.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我应该知道是谁来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.82,0:02:20.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think I know who that is
Dialogue: 1,0:02:20.72,0:02:23.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请欢迎  翼龙波蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.72,0:02:23.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please welcome the Potty-dactyl
Dialogue: 1,0:02:23.95,0:02:25.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.95,0:02:25.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry I'm late
Dialogue: 1,0:02:25.27,0:02:27.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你怎么不穿戏服
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.27,0:02:27.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why aren't you wearing your costume?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:27.41,0:02:29.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我好不容易通宵做出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.41,0:02:29.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I stayed up all night making it
Dialogue: 1,0:02:30.22,0:02:31.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你在浪费你时间  老东西
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.22,0:02:31.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're wasting your time, old man
Dialogue: 1,0:02:31.67,0:02:33.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,史前时代太土了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.67,0:02:33.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Prehistoric stuff is lame
Dialogue: 1,0:02:33.21,0:02:35.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,众所周知  未来才是王道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.21,0:02:35.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Everybody knows the future's where's it at
Dialogue: 1,0:02:35.21,0:02:36.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.21,0:02:36.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:37.21,0:02:38.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,才不对
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.21,0:02:38.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's not true
Dialogue: 1,0:02:38.60,0:02:40.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家别理他
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.60,0:02:40.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't mind him, folks
Dialogue: 1,0:02:40.14,0:02:43.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就连海绵宝宝都知道史前特别
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.14,0:02:41.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why, even SpongeBob SquarePants
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.97,0:02:43.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,knows that prehistoric stuff is
Dialogue: 1,0:02:43.87,0:02:45.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小朋友怎么说的来着
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.87,0:02:45.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do the kids say?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:45.64,0:02:46.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,酷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.64,0:02:46.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,cool
Dialogue: 1,0:02:47.04,0:02:47.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,才不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.04,0:02:47.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, he doesn't
Dialogue: 1,0:02:47.83,0:02:48.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.83,0:02:48.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, he does
Dialogue: 1,0:02:48.54,0:02:49.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.54,0:02:49.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:02:49.02,0:02:50.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,肯定知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.02,0:02:50.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He most certainly does
Dialogue: 1,0:02:50.21,0:02:50.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,才不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.21,0:02:50.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, he doesn't
Dialogue: 3,0:02:50.79,0:02:51.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他知道
Dialogue: 2,0:02:50.79,0:02:51.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, he does
Dialogue: 3,0:02:51.51,0:02:52.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 2,0:02:51.51,0:02:52.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:02:52.11,0:02:54.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我知道他肯定知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.11,0:02:54.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know for a fact that he does
Dialogue: 1,0:02:54.02,0:02:54.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.02,0:02:54.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.78,0:02:57.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,75,,同时
Dialogue: 1,0:02:59.45,0:03:00.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.45,0:03:00.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:03:00.45,0:03:01.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.45,0:03:01.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:01.45,0:03:03.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,说不清  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.45,0:03:03.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't know, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:03:03.42,0:03:05.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但我有种特别奇怪的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.42,0:03:05.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But I've got the strangest feeling
Dialogue: 1,0:03:05.60,0:03:09.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,某处有个海盗跟鹦鹉在吵我的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.60,0:03:07.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that somewhere a pirate and parrot
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.50,0:03:09.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,are arguing about me
Dialogue: 1,0:03:09.39,0:03:10.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,鹦鹉快吵赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.39,0:03:10.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And the parrot is winning
Dialogue: 1,0:03:10.87,0:03:11.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.87,0:03:11.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Does
Dialogue: 1,0:03:11.56,0:03:11.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.56,0:03:11.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Doesn't
Dialogue: 1,0:03:11.94,0:03:12.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.94,0:03:12.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Does
Dialogue: 1,0:03:12.27,0:03:12.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.27,0:03:12.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Doesn't
Dialogue: 1,0:03:12.72,0:03:13.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.72,0:03:13.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Does
Dialogue: 1,0:03:13.15,0:03:13.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.15,0:03:13.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Doesn't
Dialogue: 1,0:03:13.59,0:03:14.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.59,0:03:14.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Does
Dialogue: 1,0:03:14.53,0:03:15.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们吵架期间呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.53,0:03:15.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look, while we're arguing
Dialogue: 1,0:03:15.97,0:03:17.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要不你们就来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.97,0:03:17.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,why don't you folks go ahead
