Dialogue: 1,0:13:38.64,0:13:39.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,进来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.64,0:13:39.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on
Dialogue: 1,0:13:39.82,0:13:43.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小朋友  我是在一大块冰里找到他的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.82,0:13:43.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You see, kids, I found him frozen in a block of ice
Dialogue: 1,0:13:43.05,0:13:44.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后我又花了三天的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.05,0:13:44.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and then I spent three days
Dialogue: 1,0:13:44.57,0:13:46.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,用我妈的吹风机帮他解冻
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.57,0:13:46.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,thawing him out with my mom's hair dryer
Dialogue: 1,0:13:46.90,0:13:48.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我给他取名叫洞哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.90,0:13:48.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I call him Cavey
Dialogue: 1,0:13:49.79,0:13:50.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是不是很厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.79,0:13:50.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Isn't he something?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:51.06,0:13:52.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没事的  洞哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.06,0:13:52.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's okay, Cavey
Dialogue: 1,0:13:54.81,0:13:56.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,微不足道  老东西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.81,0:13:56.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's nothing, Old Timer
Dialogue: 1,0:13:56.37,0:13:57.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给未来让个道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.37,0:13:57.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Make way for the future
Dialogue: 1,0:13:58.67,0:13:59.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.67,0:13:59.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Greetings
Dialogue: 1,0:13:59.70,0:14:02.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是X29488
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.70,0:14:02.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am the X29488
Dialogue: 1,0:14:02.47,0:14:04.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,需要什么服务
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.47,0:14:04.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How may I serve you?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:07.15,0:14:09.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你上哪找来那么多破玩意的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.15,0:14:09.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where do you keep getting all this stuff?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:09.70,0:14:10.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,关你屁事  老东西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.70,0:14:10.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Never you mind, Pops
Dialogue: 1,0:14:10.93,0:14:12.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不如看洞哥怎么说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.93,0:14:12.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's go see what Cavey thinks
Dialogue: 1,0:14:16.89,0:14:18.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,进攻
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.89,0:14:18.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Attack
Dialogue: 1,0:14:24.97,0:14:26.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,波蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.97,0:14:26.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Potty
Dialogue: 1,0:14:27.05,0:14:28.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你把我的原始人节目毁了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.05,0:14:28.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're ruining my caveman show
Dialogue: 1,0:14:28.99,0:14:30.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,进攻
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.99,0:14:30.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Attack
Dialogue: 1,0:14:31.43,0:14:34.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派斯还能夺回特辑的主动权吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.43,0:14:34.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Will Patchy ever get control of the special?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:34.52,0:14:36.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝会用火做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.52,0:14:36.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What will SpongeBob do with fire?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:36.35,0:14:39.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,继续收看海绵史传
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.35,0:14:39.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stay tuned to SpongeBob SquarePants B.C.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.43,0:14:40.27,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(724.006,208)}海绵史传
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.43,0:14:40.27,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(323.45,842)}史前笑传
Dialogue: 1,0:14:39.24,0:14:40.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.24,0:14:40.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and find out
Dialogue: 1,0:14:41.42,0:14:44.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,欢迎继续收看海绵史传
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.42,0:14:44.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Welcome back to SpongeBob SquarePants B.C.
Dialogue: 1,0:14:44.67,0:14:47.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派斯这边的情况变得一发不可收拾了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.67,0:14:45.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sounds like things have gone
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.94,0:14:47.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,from bad to worse for Patchy
Dialogue: 1,0:14:47.54,0:14:48.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.54,0:14:48.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let’s watch
Dialogue: 1,0:14:48.59,0:14:49.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,进攻
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.59,0:14:49.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Attack
Dialogue: 1,0:14:51.32,0:14:52.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太好看了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.32,0:14:52.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is great
Dialogue: 1,0:14:52.97,0:14:53.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.97,0:14:53.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ahoy
Dialogue: 1,0:14:53.57,0:14:54.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,很高兴你们回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.57,0:14:54.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Glad you're back
Dialogue: 1,0:14:55.52,0:14:57.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,继续看完海绵史传吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.52,0:14:57.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's watch the rest of SpongeBob B.C.
Dialogue: 1,0:14:57.86,0:14:59.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我先把事情收拾干净
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.86,0:14:59.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,while I get things straightened out around here
Dialogue: 1,0:15:02.70,0:15:03.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.70,0:15:03.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Or
Dialogue: 1,0:15:03.60,0:15:04.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可能收拾不了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.60,0:15:04.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,maybe not
Dialogue: 1,0:15:04.64,0:15:06.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,进攻
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.64,0:15:06.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Attack
Dialogue: 1,0:15:06.71,0:15:09.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,先前我们看到这群饿肚子原始人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.71,0:15:09.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,When we last saw our hungry troglodytes
Dialogue: 1,0:15:09.47,0:15:11.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,刚刚发现了火
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.47,0:15:11.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,they'd just discovered fire
Dialogue: 1,0:15:11.12,0:15:13.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们还要多久才会搞出烂摊子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.12,0:15:13.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How long will it take for them to mess it up?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:13.36,0:15:14.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一起看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.36,0:15:14.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's see
