Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.77,0:19:23.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, SpongeGar
Dialogue: 1,0:19:31.32,0:19:33.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好你个小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.32,0:19:33.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sutaka jakasa
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.32,0:19:33.27,注释,,0,0,0,,[ Sutaka jakasa：Why you little ]
Dialogue: 1,0:19:37.41,0:19:39.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的不是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.41,0:19:39.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tabanga-do
Dialogue: 1,0:19:46.22,0:19:48.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也许某些历史事件
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.22,0:19:48.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Perhaps certain events in history
Dialogue: 1,0:19:48.76,0:19:51.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还是不说比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.76,0:19:51.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,are better left untold
Dialogue: 1,0:19:56.00,0:19:58.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在我能理解章鱼哥什么感受了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.00,0:19:58.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now I know how Squidward feels
Dialogue: 1,0:19:58.79,0:20:00.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,干嘛苦瓜脸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.79,0:20:00.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why the long face?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:00.19,0:20:03.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你自己心知肚明  你个坏鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.19,0:20:01.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think you know
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.09,0:20:03.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,perfectly well, you little wingèd vermin
Dialogue: 1,0:20:03.65,0:20:06.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就只想给各位观众看看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.65,0:20:06.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All I wanted was to show the nice people
Dialogue: 1,0:20:06.28,0:20:08.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,原始人有多厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.28,0:20:08.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,how great the cavemen were
Dialogue: 1,0:20:08.16,0:20:11.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,结果放出来的全是高科技惹的祸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.16,0:20:11.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But all they got was technology-induced chaos
Dialogue: 1,0:20:11.83,0:20:13.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快进来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.83,0:20:13.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come back inside
Dialogue: 1,0:20:13.00,0:20:15.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你一定会特别惊喜的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.00,0:20:15.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think you'll be pleasantly surprised
Dialogue: 1,0:20:15.31,0:20:17.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你把机器人赶走了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.31,0:20:17.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You got rid of the robot android cyborg?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:17.48,0:20:18.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对  比那强
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.48,0:20:18.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, even better
Dialogue: 1,0:20:19.77,0:20:22.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,波蒂  我应该是真的看错你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.77,0:20:22.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Potty, I guess I really misjudged you
Dialogue: 1,0:20:22.87,0:20:23.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.87,0:20:23.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What the?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:26.78,0:20:28.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,当世界相撞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.78,0:20:28.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,When worlds collide
Dialogue: 1,0:20:28.66,0:20:29.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是不是很棒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.66,0:20:29.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pretty sweet, eh?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:31.00,0:20:32.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以逃得走
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.00,0:20:32.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can run
Dialogue: 1,0:20:32.11,0:20:33.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但是躲不掉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.11,0:20:33.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but you can't hide
Dialogue: 1,0:20:33.83,0:20:34.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,当世界相撞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.83,0:20:34.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,When worlds collide
Dialogue: 1,0:20:35.13,0:20:36.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,会变特好笑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.13,0:20:36.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You'll laugh so hard
Dialogue: 1,0:20:36.25,0:20:37.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以笑死你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.25,0:20:37.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You'll swear you've died
Dialogue: 1,0:20:37.60,0:20:38.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,当世界相撞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.60,0:20:38.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,When worlds collide
Dialogue: 1,0:20:38.63,0:20:41.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,牵住我的手  让我当导游
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.63,0:20:41.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hold my hand, I'll be your guide
Dialogue: 1,0:20:41.10,0:20:42.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,当世界相撞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.10,0:20:42.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,When worlds collide
Dialogue: 1,0:20:42.88,0:20:44.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,系好  系好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.88,0:20:44.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Buckle, buckle
Dialogue: 1,0:20:44.07,0:20:46.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,系好安全带  一起去路上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.07,0:20:46.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,buckle up for the sweetest ride
Dialogue: 1,0:20:46.10,0:20:48.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快准备好要来欣喜若狂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.10,0:20:48.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And prepare to have your mind blown wide
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.14,0:20:50.93,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(717.997,568)}当世界相撞
Dialogue: 1,0:20:48.39,0:20:49.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,当世界相撞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.39,0:20:49.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,When worlds collide
Dialogue: 1,0:20:51.64,0:20:52.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来看看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.64,0:20:52.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Check it out
Dialogue: 1,0:20:52.31,0:20:54.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,当世界相撞  有点不寻常
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.31,0:20:54.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,When worlds collide, it's a curious thing
Dialogue: 1,0:20:54.40,0:20:56.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,机器人原始人合唱前所未见
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.40,0:20:56.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bet you never heard a robot and a caveman sing
Dialogue: 1,0:20:56.73,0:20:59.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他的金属胸膛里面尽是些零件
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.73,0:20:59.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,In his metal chest are some working parts
Dialogue: 1,0:20:59.12,0:21:01.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟我的心脏又能有啥不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.12,0:21:01.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How is that different from my beating heart?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:06.87,0:21:07.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来自未来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.87,0:21:07.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm from the future
Dialogue: 1,0:21:07.99,0:21:09.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来自过去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.99,0:21:09.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And I'm from the past
Dialogue: 1,0:21:09.08,0:21:10.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不代表这场友情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.08,0:21:10.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But that don't mean this friendship
Dialogue: 1,0:21:10.22,0:21:11.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,维持不下去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.22,0:21:11.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wasn't built to last
Dialogue: 1,0:21:11.33,0:21:12.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,实验室里造了他
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.33,0:21:12.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He was made in a lab
Dialogue: 1,0:21:12.48,0:21:13.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,山洞里生了我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.48,0:21:13.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And I was born in a cave
Dialogue: 1,0:21:13.83,0:21:16.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这场跨时代锐舞会让你欢呼尖叫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.83,0:21:16.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So let me hear you holler for this inter-era rave
Dialogue: 1,0:21:19.46,0:21:21.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,未来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.46,0:21:21.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Future
Dialogue: 1,0:21:25.68,0:21:26.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,支持
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.68,0:21:26.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Word
Dialogue: 1,0:21:27.18,0:21:28.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是机器宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.18,0:21:28.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am SpongeTron
Dialogue: 1,0:21:28.51,0:21:29.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可  可
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.51,0:21:29.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You, you
Dialogue: 1,0:21:29.51,0:21:30.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以逃得走
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.51,0:21:30.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you can run
Dialogue: 1,0:21:32.18,0:21:33.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但是躲不掉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.18,0:21:33.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But you can't hide
Dialogue: 1,0:21:37.17,0:21:38.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,当世界相撞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.17,0:21:38.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,When worlds collide
Dialogue: 1,0:21:41.15,0:21:43.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,波蒂  你说得确实
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.15,0:21:43.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, Potty, I guess you were right
Dialogue: 1,0:21:43.52,0:21:45.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,未来的确很酷
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.52,0:21:45.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The future is cool
Dialogue: 1,0:21:45.47,0:21:47.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只是想让你别太在意
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.47,0:21:47.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just to show you there's no hard feelings
Dialogue: 1,0:21:47.22,0:21:49.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要送你份史前大礼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.22,0:21:49.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got you a present from the prehistoric times
Dialogue: 1,0:21:49.87,0:21:51.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么礼物  新遮羞布吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.87,0:21:51.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What is it, a new loincloth?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:51.67,0:21:52.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,错
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.67,0:21:52.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:21:52.17,0:21:53.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,超大额骨吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.17,0:21:53.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,An enlarged forehead?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:53.60,0:21:54.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,错
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.60,0:21:54.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:21:54.97,0:21:55.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那又是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.97,0:21:55.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:00.75,0:22:01.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,波蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.75,0:22:01.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Potty
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.09,0:22:08.18,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1200.668,894)}冷饮
Dialogue: 1,0:22:05.77,0:22:06.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太好看了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.77,0:22:06.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is great
Dialogue: 1,0:22:13.62,0:22:16.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,感谢小朋友们收看海绵史传
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.62,0:22:16.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, thanks for watching SpongeBob B.C., kids
Dialogue: 1,0:22:16.87,0:22:17.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.87,0:22:17.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bye
Dialogue: 1,0:22:19.90,0:22:21.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在还挠痒痒了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.90,0:22:21.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now he's tickling
Dialogue: 1,0:22:22.30,0:22:24.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别闹了  小坏蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.30,0:22:24.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Cut it out, you rascal
